        <ontology:partOfNarrative rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/narrative/N235_VC_13_SCA"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/63.44_10.4"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/0"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The reference mountain chain of this VC is Scandinavean Mountains - Scandes. The reference mountain landscape of this VC is Stjørdal. The MRL is crossed by the Stjørdalselva river until its arrival to the Trondheim fiord. The Eastern part of the municipality belongs to the Skarvan and Roltdalen National Park. Due to its proximity to Trondheim, the municipality is developing an urbanization process. Simultaneously, there are still multiple local VCs within the AUK - SMAKER FRA STJØRDALSFØRET, such as organic vegetable farming, family dairies, beekeeping , eggs, beer brewery, traditional bakery, coffee distillery, and rural touristic accommodation.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


